---
const whatsapp = "553298408646";
---
<section id="contato" class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-6 py-14 md:py-20 scroll-mt-24">
    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-center text-green-700 mb-6">Fale com a DivComp</h2>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 text-center mb-8">
        Precisa de ajuda agora? Fale direto no WhatsApp ou envie uma mensagem pelo formulário.
    </p>
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4 mb-6">
        <a href={`https://wa.me/${whatsapp}`} target="_blank" rel="noopener"
           class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-green-600 hover:bg-green-700 text-white font-bold px-8 py-4 rounded-lg shadow-lg text-lg transition">
            <span class="icon-[mdi--whatsapp] w-7 h-7"></span>
            WhatsApp
        </a>
        <a href="mailto:contato@divcomp.com.br"
           class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-white hover:bg-green-50 text-green-700 border border-green-600 font-bold px-8 py-4 rounded-lg shadow-lg text-lg transition">
            <span class="icon-[ic--baseline-email] w-7 h-7"></span>
            E-mail
        </a>
    </div>
    {/* Exemplo de formulário simples */}
    <form class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow p-6 flex flex-col gap-4">
        <input type="text" name="nome" placeholder="Seu nome" class="border rounded px-4 py-2" required />
        <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Seu e-mail" class="border rounded px-4 py-2" required />
        <textarea name="mensagem" placeholder="Sua mensagem" class="border rounded px-4 py-2" required></textarea>
        <button type="submit" class="bg-green-600 hover:bg-green-700 text-white font-bold px-6 py-3 rounded transition">
            Enviar Mensagem
        </button>
    </form>
</section>
